author: stefan2
msg: Continue migrating FSX to the two-pool paradigm.  Many single-pool functions
don't allocate a return value, i.e. their pools can immediately be renamed
to SCRATCH_POOL.  Do this for revprops.* .
svn_fs_x__packed_revprop_available): POOL is actually a SCRATCH_POOL.
